name: THE MORNING RUSH
description:
Enjoy and Rate :D
Sorry for it not showing the stress bar nor the time limit UI but that's due to the small time limit and us overestimating our time left. (This can hopefully be fixed by pressing the full screen button)

Hopefully you can oversee those errors and enjoy the game still.

A special thanks to https://la-prise-peritel.itch.io/ and https://gulky.itch.io/ for contributing massively to the project
